// ░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░
// OASIS DATABASE SCHEMA — SQLite local-first
// The single source of truth for missions, memory, and agent state
// ░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░

generator client {
  provider = "prisma-client-js"
  output   = "../node_modules/.prisma/client"
}

datasource db {
  provider = "sqlite"
  url      = env("DATABASE_URL")
}

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// MISSION — The atomic unit of work
// SCORE = (actualSeconds / 60) × VALOR × PRIORITY
// PRIORITY = (urgency × easiness × impact) / 125
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

model Mission {
  id             Int       @id @default(autoincrement())
  name           String
  description    String?
  status         String    @default("todo") // todo | wip | done | archived
  queuePosition  Int?      // null = unqueued, 1-based for active queue

  // Priority Triangle
  urgency        Float     @default(5) // 1-10
  easiness       Float     @default(5) // 1-10
  impact         Float     @default(5) // 1-10
  priority       Float     @default(1) // (U×E×I)/125

  // Scoring
  valor          Float?    // 0.0-2.0 self-assessment of focus/quality
  score          Float?    // final: (mins × valor × priority)

  // Time Tracking
  startedAt      DateTime?
  endedAt        DateTime?
  createdAt      DateTime  @default(now())
  updatedAt      DateTime  @updatedAt
  horizon        String?   // 'fixed' | 'open' | null
  targetSeconds  Int?      // budget for fixed horizon
  isPaused       Boolean   @default(false)
  pausedAt       DateTime?
  totalPausedMs  Int       @default(0)
  actualSeconds  Int?      // real work time
  isIRL          Boolean   @default(false) // offline/physical work

  // Maturation (curator pipeline)
  // 0=para 1=pashyanti 2=madhyama 3=vaikhari 4=built 5=reviewed 6=tested 7=gamertested 8=carbontested
  maturityLevel  Int       @default(0)
  assignedTo     String?   // 'carbondev' | 'anorak' | 'parzival' | null
  executionMode  String?   // 'crispr' (worktree) | 'builder' (direct) — set by curator

  // Specs (curator-enriched)
  carbonDescription   String? // human-language war cry (vibes, emotions, analogies)
  siliconDescription  String? // technical spec for coder (the bible)
  acceptanceCriteria  String? // what "done" means (baked into siliconDescription too)

  // Curator scoring (RL signal)
  flawlessPercent     Float?  // 0-100 curator's execution confidence
  reviewerScore       Float?  // 0-100 first-pass reviewer score
  testerScore         Float?  // 0-100 first-pass tester score
  gamerScore          Float?  // 0-100 first-pass gamer score
  gamerVerdict        String? // 'PASS' | 'FAIL' | 'BLOCKED'

  // Curator queue (separate from devcraft queue)
  curatorQueuePosition Int?   // null = not in curator queue

  // Execution checkpoint (DB recovery after crash)
  executionPhase      String? // 'coding' | 'reviewing' | 'testing' | null
  executionRound      Int     @default(0) // which coder→reviewer round

  // History Thread — JSON array of HistoryEntry objects
  // { timestamp, actor, action, curatorMsg?, silicondevMsg?, verdict?, rating?, ... }
  history        String?   // full lifecycle log (curator, carbondev, coder, reviewer, tester)
  notes          String?   // legacy / free-text notes

  // Mission image (curator-generated battle flag)
  imageUrl       String?   // URL or path to generated mission image

  // Dharma (Noble Eightfold Path of the Oasis)
  dharmaPath     String?   // comma-separated: view,intention,speech,action,livelihood,effort,mindfulness,concentration
  questName      String?   // parent quest/yatra name

  @@index([status])
  @@index([queuePosition])
  @@index([maturityLevel])
  @@index([assignedTo])
  @@index([curatorQueuePosition])
}

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// MEMORY — Structured key-value knowledge persistence
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

model Memory {
  id        Int      @id @default(autoincrement())
  category  String   // preference | habit | goal | fact | pattern
  key       String
  value     String
  createdAt DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt DateTime @updatedAt

  @@unique([category, key])
  @@index([category])
}

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// WORLD — 3D world with full state as JSON
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

model World {
  id              String    @id @default(cuid())
  userId          String    @default("local-user")
  name            String    @default("The Forge")
  icon            String    @default("🌍")
  visibility      String    @default("private") // private | public | unlisted | public_edit

  data            String?   // JSON: full WorldState (catalog objects, crafted scenes, conjured assets, sky, ground)
  creatorName     String?
  creatorAvatar   String?

  visitCount      Int       @default(0)
  objectCount     Int       @default(0)
  thumbnailUrl    String?

  createdAt       DateTime  @default(now())
  updatedAt       DateTime  @updatedAt

  snapshots       WorldSnapshot[]

  @@index([userId])
  @@index([visibility])
}

model WorldSnapshot {
  id              String    @id @default(cuid())
  worldId         String
  world           World     @relation(fields: [worldId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  data            String?   // JSON: full WorldState
  objectCount     Int       @default(0)
  source          String    @default("auto") // auto | manual

  createdAt       DateTime  @default(now())

  @@index([worldId, createdAt])
}

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// JOURNAL — Sacred timestamped reflections
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

model Journal {
  id        Int      @id @default(autoincrement())
  content   String
  tags      String?  // JSON: string[]
  mood      String?
  createdAt DateTime @default(now())
}

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// CURATOR LOG — Per-invocation tracking for Anorak Pro's curator
// "The garden tender's journal"
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

model CuratorLog {
  id                Int       @id @default(autoincrement())
  status            String    @default("running") // running, completed, failed

  startedAt         DateTime  @default(now())
  endedAt           DateTime?
  durationMs        Int?

  // Cost
  tokensIn          Int       @default(0)
  tokensOut         Int       @default(0)

  // Results
  missionsProcessed Int       @default(0)
  missionsEnriched  Int       @default(0)
  missionResults    String?   // JSON: per-mission enrichment results

  // Error
  error             String?

  @@index([status])
  @@index([startedAt])
}

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// CARBON MODEL — Training pairs for Player 1 prediction
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

model CarbonModelEntry {
  id                Int      @id @default(autoincrement())
  missionId         Int?
  missionName       String?
  context           String   // what prompted this prediction
  predictedResponse String   // what the model thought Player 1 would say
  actualResponse    String?  // what Player 1 actually said (null = pending)
  accepted          Boolean?
  rating            Int?     // 0-10
  confidence        Float?   // 0.0-1.0
  decision          String?  // bump | refine | other
  createdAt         DateTime @default(now())

  @@index([missionId])
}

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// PROFILE — Local-first user profile (single row per userId)
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

model Profile {
  id            Int      @id @default(autoincrement())
  userId        String   @unique @default("local-user")
  displayName   String   @default("Player 1")
  bio           String?
  avatarUrl     String?
  avatar3dUrl   String?
  totalXp       Int      @default(0)
  level         Int      @default(1)
  aura          Int      @default(0)
  lastLoginDate String?  // ISO date string 'YYYY-MM-DD'
  createdAt     DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt     DateTime @updatedAt
}

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// TOKEN BURN — Per-source aggregated token usage tracking
// Aggregated by source + time window (hourly buckets)
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

model TokenBurn {
  id           Int      @id @default(autoincrement())
  source       String   // 'anorak' | 'anorak-pro-chat' | 'anorak-pro-curator' | etc.
  inputTokens  Int      @default(0)
  outputTokens Int      @default(0)
  window       String   // ISO hour bucket: '2026-03-28T14' (hourly aggregation key)
  createdAt    DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt    DateTime @updatedAt

  @@unique([source, window])
  @@index([source])
  @@index([window])
}
